Package: blouch
Title: Bayesian Linear Ornstein-Uhlenbeck models for Comparative
    Hypotheses
Version: 1.0.0
Authors@R: 
    person("Mark", "Grabowski", , "mark.walter.grabowski@gmail.com", role = c("aut", "cre"),
           comment = c(ORCID = "0000-0001-7045-9472"))
Description: Blouch: Bayesian Linear Ornstein-Uhlenbeck models for Comparative Hypotheses fits adaptive models of continuous trait evolution in a Bayesian framework based on categorical or continuous predictors, incorporates measurement error. Blouch includes new implementations of Ornstein-Ulenbeck models including allowing for varying effects (varying intercepts and varying slopes), multilevel modeling, and non-centered models.
